    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "victoriametrics-logs-datasource",
        "uid": "victorialogs"
      },
      "description": "Chronological tool calls for the selected Linear issue (across all sessions). call_number is the global sequence number. Dedicated columns surface the key tool_input field for each tool (command / file_path / pattern / query / skill / args / url / description); the raw tool_input column stays available as a fallback for tools with other free-form inputs such as Edit, Write, TodoWrite, and Agent.",
